Output taso-demo.gif

Set Shell powershell
Require ffmpeg

Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1000
Set Height 550
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set Margin 20
Set BorderRadius 8
Set WindowBar Colorful

Hide
Type "clear"
Enter
Sleep 500ms
Show

Type "taso --help"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "taso ghost"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "taso drift"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "taso score"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 4s

Sleep 1s